READ_0700063,《逆天五行論》作者：佚名
崇萬物五行，為四季基準；
縱常理無存，然命不可違。
機存萬物中，亦生萬物外；
尋尋覓覓十，行言外之意。,《逆天五行论》作者：佚名
崇万物五行，为四季基准；
纵常理无存，然命不可违。
机存万物中，亦生万物外；
寻寻觅觅十，行言外之意。

Items.mt:
The Theory of the Five Elements of the Heavenly Reverse by Anonymous <<
>>The five elements of all things are the basis of the four seasons; <<
>>Even though common sense does not exist, fate cannot be violated. <<
>>The machine exists in all things, and is also born outside of all things; <<
>>searching for ten, and doing what is beyond words.
